definitions.dict_definition:
@khướu
- Chinese laughing-thrush (chim)
=Hót như khướu+To be an inveterate flatterer, to be a toady

@khư khư
- Grip, clutch
=Ôm khư khư+To grip something in one's arms

@khước từ
* verb
- to refuse; to decline

@khước
- (cũ) Luck bestowed by a deity, blessing
=Đi lấy lộc ngày tết lấy khước+To go and pluck tree buds at tet for luck
